失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"c686cbc1f6e35b4d93dc3ae76d7c90accbaacfac","tid":1627171,"uid":28941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"越多哨兵，情報spread得越快，勇武越安全"},{"pid":"cf9ffc4df5f27fa80d4bd2e0cf9f13fe3b7883f1","tid":1627171,"uid":28941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"越多哨兵，情報spread得越快，勇武越安全"},{"pid":"02596c03fc3ae99354b2c1b74808bac03255ba79","tid":1627171,"uid":28941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:55:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">越多哨兵，情報spread得越快，勇武越安全</span></span>"},{"pid":"ebff35eee84fe0721a13aa84edb41b50d87c560d","tid":1627171,"uid":28941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">越多哨兵，情報spread得越快，勇武越安全</span></span>"},{"pid":"cba533b81c132edcc7c662cf76fb3084be4aaf0f","tid":1627171,"uid":28941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:56:29.000Z","msg":"越多哨兵，情報spread得越快，勇武越安全"},{"pid":"ffad870c0259a17e4067c3559bb78f3a0d00a559","tid":1627171,"uid":28941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1084e5b108f65547e9c5cb77b598a46428a4a317","tid":1627171,"uid":28941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:57:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3708a4e5b4392d6e3e53a10d96f5cdaf7d6e18b4","tid":1627171,"uid":28941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"pish"},